summary: Formerly a Veterinarian with now 7 years of experience in creating value on a B2B setting in start-ups, scale-ups and large multinationals. Since 2018, my focus has been enabling data-driven decision making for firms and their customers. In consequence, in 2021 I obtained my MSc in Data Science and Marketing Analytics while starting a career in this growing field. My main purpose now is to combine strong communicational skills and a scientific background to achieve change and growth.
